ovt. will transfer this amount directly into the bank account of girls. Thus, girls can utilize this money on their own.", "005-normal": "This scheme will benefit around 6 lakh families and govt. will spend Rs. 1500 crore for its successful implementation. Furthermore, Rupashree scheme will reduce the financial burden of poor families."}}